k and serve immediately."}],"hintsAndTricks":["This dish is best served immediately, however you can cut out the watermelon rounds in advance and store in the refrigerator for 1-2 hours before making the salmon ceviche. It is not advisable to prepare the ceviche component in advance as citric acid in the lime juice may overcook the salmon."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","30m","25 pieces"]}